data.description: Fabulous three bedroom home in Summer Chase features a newly remodeled kitchen and plenty of room for entertaining. The home has tile throughout the living areas and wood laminate floors in the bedrooms. Summer Chase states it is a community for 55+ adults. Included in the maintenance is CABLE with Premium Channels, Lawn Care, Security Alarm Monitoring, Common Grounds and Clubhouse. The community features a gated entry, tennis courts, social hall, card rooms, bocce ball courts and shuffle broad.
